fields.name: ID
fields.formula:
concat( 
  left(join(field("Created by"),""), 1), 
  regex_replace( 
    totext( 
      field("Date and time reported") 
    ), 
    "(-|:|\s|\t)", 
    "" 
  ), 
  row_id() 
)

fields.name: Week reported
fields.formula:
concat( 
  "üå± Week ", 
  field("Week number in the year"), 
  " of ", 
  totext(year(field("Date and time reported"))) 
)

fields.name: Week number in the year
